This version of ledstats is based on ledstatus 0.1 by Jeremy Garff.
It uses libparportled to run.

Julien Danjou
<julien@jdanjou.org>

The device used:
                                pin 20 (ground)
                                  |
               150ohm     LED     |
pin 2 (D0) ----/\/\/------|>|-----+
                                  |
pin 3 (D1) ----/\/\/------|>|-----+
                                  |
pin 4 (D2) ----/\/\/------|>|-----+

            [...]
                                  |
pin 9 (D7) ----/\/\/------|>|-----+


